OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be dry with lengthy
OL,6,Fbright or sunny spells and feeling
OL,7,Fslightly warmer. Sunshine turning hazy
OL,8,Flater in the afternoon as high cloud
OL,9,Fspreads southeast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry at first with some hazy
OL,12,Fevening sunshine. Clouding over
OL,13,Fthrough the evening and overnight with
OL,14,Fsome patchy light rain.
OL,15,
OL,16,CMonday:FIt will be cloudy to start the
OL,17,Fday with some patchy rain. Turning
OL,18,Fdrier, brighter through the afternoon
OL,19,Fwith some sunny spells at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
