OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fwith patchy light rain in the
OL,7,Fmornings, before warm sunny intervals
OL,8,Fdevelop through the afternoons.
OL,9,FBecoming quite breezy on Thursday.
